00:02:11,458 --> 00:02:14,500
Morning, Ritsuka. Smells good.

26
00:02:14,583 --> 00:02:16,458
Morning, Mom. Sleep well?

27
00:02:16,541 --> 00:02:17,916
Or did you work all night?

28
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,375
[MARIA]
Worked all night.

29
